					<description><![CDATA[What?  It&#8217;s my site. I can a share something that&#8217;s just plain silly now and then.  Besides, I love TimH.  Enjoy this random bit of fun from 2013 that just happens to have &#8220;Twist&#8221; in the title.  Even if it&#8217;s actually about film plot twists.  Whatever. There&#8217;s an elf in the corner.]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><iframe src="//www.youtube.com/embed/fvT7tagYBJU" width="560" height="315" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen="allowfullscreen"></iframe><br />
What?  It&#8217;s my site. I can a share something that&#8217;s just plain silly now and then.  Besides, I love TimH.  Enjoy this random bit of fun from 2013 that just happens to have &#8220;Twist&#8221; in the title.  Even if it&#8217;s actually about film plot twists.  Whatever.</p>
<p>There&#8217;s an elf in the corner.</p>
